div.p: This is Router1 (R1), sending my first Hello packet now that OSPF is enabled. I'm introducing myself and initiating the process to establish communication.
I will continue sending Hello packets periodically to multicast address 224.0.0.5. I look forward to hearing from you to form an OSPF adjacency.
